# Sample Tickets

## Ticket #001 - Slow Computer
Issue: User reported the computer was running slowly.  
Resolution: Reviewed Task Manager, identified high resource usage, and closed unnecessary applications.

---

## Ticket #002 - Network Connectivity Issue
Issue: User reported internet problems.  
Resolution: Verified adapter status, confirmed IP address, tested connectivity, and confirmed DNS resolution.

---

## Ticket #003 - Password Reset / Account Support
Issue: User needed account assistance.  
Resolution: Verified local account and reviewed password management options.

---

## Ticket #004 - Printer Troubleshooting
Issue: User reported printer problems.  
Resolution: Reviewed printers, queues, and Print Spooler service settings.
